Implementation for Syntax Simplification 

** openbook-syntax-service 
The main module containing the Web service wrappers.
Provides SOAP1.1 web service using JAX-WS and Apache CXF2.
The web service consume/return a string parameter containing a GATE xml document.

** openbook-syntax-war
The module which packages the Web service as a war file compatible with Apache Tomcat
Soon: Metro compatible war packaging

** openbook-syntax-client
Command line client to invoke the endpoint

